# .gitignore — br-ai-context-kit (skeleton)
#
# The entries below are the per-app / internal files removed from the skeleton. Onboarding regenerates
# them into this tree, so keep them ignored — nothing here should ever reach the public repo.

# --- internal planning (not part of the published kit) ---
/DEV_PLAN.md

# --- LSP internal build artifacts (whole folder excluded) ---
/lsp/

# --- per-app onboarding output: generated & confidential, never commit ---
/app/architecture.md
/app/data-model.md
/app/data-model.json
/app/data-model-index.json
/app/conventions.md
/app/exemplars/

# --- forward-looking hygiene for clones that onboard/compile a real app ---
# (not part of the diff; safe to trim. compiled BR objects + node deps)
*.br
*.bro
*.wb
*.wbo
node_modules/
